  <p>This is an educational breakdown of Selank covering its mechanisms, clinical research, dosing protocols, and safety profile. It is <strong>not a recommendation to use Selank</strong>. Selank is not FDA-approved in the United States. Consult a qualified healthcare provider before considering any peptide regimen.</p>
