<!-- ========== SELANK VS TRADITIONAL ANXIOLYTICS ========== -->
<hr class="sep">
<h2>Selank vs. Traditional Anxiolytics</h2>

<p>The comparison against conventional anxiety medications is where Selank's advantages become most apparent. Traditional options carry serious trade-offs that Selank largely avoids.</p>

