  <p>This comparison isn't suggesting Selank is a replacement for prescribed anxiety medications. SSRIs and benzodiazepines have strong clinical evidence and serve important roles. The table highlights Selank's <strong>different</strong> trade-off profile, not its superiority as a blanket treatment.</p>
</div>

<!-- ========== SIDE EFFECTS ========== -->
<hr class="sep">
<h2>Side Effects and Safety</h2>

<p>Selank's safety profile is one of its strongest selling points. Russian clinical data spanning years of pharmaceutical use shows minimal adverse effects at therapeutic doses.</p>

